-- Blockbuster Wins Bankruptcy Court Approval to Borrow $25 Million of Loan
-- B y   D a v i d   M c L a u g h l i n
-- 2010-09-27T14:52:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/blockbuster-wins-bankruptcy-court-approval-to-borrow-25-million-of-loan.html
Blockbuster Inc., the movie-rental
that filed for bankruptcy last week, won court approval to
borrow an additional $25 million of a loan as it restructures,
bringing its allowed borrowing under the loan to $45 million.  To contact the reporter on this story:
